lines.text: He wanted to know why I had a tee-tee...
Pardon me? I don't know what a tee-tee is.
A vagina.
Oh, it's a pet expression of yours.
tee-tee, tinkle, po-po, wee-wee, kee-kee, poo-poo.
I had never heard tee-tee before.
What expression do you use with your children?
Vagina.
My DARLING, you did NOT cheat, you TOLD me about it. If you HADN'T told me about it, THAT would have been cheating!
When we come right up to the sex, you become embarrassed.
What am I... What would you like... What am I supposed to think?
I have no wants. Say what you think you'd like to say.
Do you think I need this? Do you really think you can help me?
I think it'd be useful to talk some more. I don't know for sure if I can help you or not. Do you think you can help yourself?
Ted is a very nervous man! Now sex is very important to a man! You know that!
Well, it seems that our time is up for today.
First, we'll have an orgy. Then we'll go see Tony Bennett.
Well look at you, man. You've got the guilt anyway. Don't waste it.
Now, do you wanna do it just like that with no feeling on my part?
Yeah.
